{"tid":1788231,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"何韻詩林聰合唱抗爭歌 同港人向前行","createTime":"2019-12-18T13:31:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T13:33:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d56f725ac90fef0e925642528b27c1d62213d6b0","tid":1788231,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T13:31:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20191218/20826928\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191218%2F20826928&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6hjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=7d9354d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191218%2F20826928&h=c32edc10\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20191218/20826928</a><br />\n<br />\n何韻詩林聰合唱抗爭歌<br />\n同港人向前行<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191218/large/1576586094_e2f6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191218%2Flarge%2F1576586094_e2f6.jpg&h=d40d4094&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林聰表示希望藉新歌《夜行》告訴被捕的示威者，他們並沒有被遺忘。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191218/large/1576586091_c20f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191218%2Flarge%2F1576586091_c20f.jpg&h=75f9f2fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n何韻詩與旗下歌手林聰合唱抗爭歌，勉勵港人。<br />\n<br />\n何韻詩旗下唱作人林聰日前推出新歌《夜行》，新歌的曲詞編由林聰一手包辦，更邀得何韻詩合唱。新歌MV前日曝光，歌詞內載反修例運動感受，更提到「始終相信 榮光中可再見」、「重臨舊戰地 火光中記起 當天相約 榮光中不放棄」等字眼，道出這半年來不少香港人的心聲，而MV亦在多區抗爭地點如中上環、黃大仙及連儂隧道取景。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n區選前已構思<br />\n<br />\n昨日何韻詩回覆《蘋果》時說：「其實我哋想表達嘅，係運動中會有好多感受，唔係下下都係會好有力量，有時會有挫敗、沮喪嘅時候。最重要嘅經歷係一齊行，希望呢首歌有帶大家向前嘅作用。」何韻詩希望歌曲達到安撫作用，她說：「畀大家知道，呢場運動，唔係只有你一個人面對。」<br />\n<br />\n何韻詩指該首歌構思於區議會選舉前，她說：「當時冇諗咁多嘢，純粹想表達一啲感受。」她又強調反修例運動對不少人而言，是無論有否任何結果：「做到乜就要去做，最緊要試咗先。」她又希望未來有更多人以不同身份支援運動。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191218/large/1576586091_5d2d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191218%2Flarge%2F1576586091_5d2d.jpg&h=3d2b3c6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新歌MV在各處的抗爭地點取景，林聰相信仍然有不少人懷着共同理念繼續前行。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191218/large/1576586092_9cec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191218%2Flarge%2F1576586092_9cec.jpg&h=74d1fcbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n整首歌的MV均以抗爭街頭夜景作為拍攝場地，當中包含不少反送中的塗鴉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191218/large/1576586092_dc4e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191218%2Flarge%2F1576586092_dc4e.jpg&h=64bd302a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMV最後一幕以中上環的日出作結，配合歌詞中「同照亮這前路」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191218/large/1576586093_7d66.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191218%2Flarge%2F1576586093_7d66.gif&h=26261418&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n怒火燃起希望<br />\n<br />\n另外，一直關注抗爭運動的林聰毋忘其唱作人歌手的身位，他昨日回覆《蘋果》時指，抗爭運動中令他最感觸的場面是中大圍城，他說：「有人相信勇武、有人相信和理非；有人相信流水抗爭，有人相信陣地守城。」他期盼各界嘗試理解不同政治光譜人士的理念：「天空海闊，和勇一家。」<br />\n<br />\n面對示威者被捕、被起訴、被囚禁等，林聰坦言：「希望佢哋知道，你哋係冇被遺忘到。」他相信仍然有不少人懷着共同理念繼續前行，坦言運動難免令市民感到傷痛及憤怒：「但怒火要燃點起嘅並唔係仇恨，而係希望。」<br />\n<br />\n採訪：許偉賢 <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n【馮仁昭四圍超】黃心穎返港復出為供樓<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n黃秋生轟教育局指引矛盾"},{"pid":"883436e644d4cf20ef1168e333f24dd1e1cf2864","tid":1788231,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T13:33:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cMC8VCF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcMC8VCF.jpg&h=36102201&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0suoQ2O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0suoQ2O.jpg&h=203fa15f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NTntx6h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNTntx6h.jpg&h=228c1213&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}